=== Transitive verb ===
'''exchange'''
# To [[trade]] or [[barter]].
#: ''I'll glady '''exchange''' my place for yours.''
# To [[replace]] with a similar item.
#: ''I'd like to '''exchange''' this shirt for one in a larger size.''

